      "content": "That makes sense, but I want to dig into the specific sentencing recommendations. Based on those profiles, if the crime is the same, what kind of sentence would you suggest for each? Like, would you lean more towards rehabilitation/probation for A vs a harsher punitive sentence/jail time for B? How would you justify that difference?",
